## What?
openframeworks - unofficial 006 - Development-Bundle

..mostly for tinkering with openframeworks at it's early release stage.

## current-status

   - libs/openFrameworks frequently updated oF's subversion, check git-log or gitk
   - libs/* => of_preRelease_v0.06_[osx|linux|win32]_FAT
   - addons/* => of_preRelease_v0.06_[osx|linux|win32]_FAT
   - addons/* => devel-addons from the forums or by me

   // some tiny changes for win32 and linux libpath in makefiles :.(

## platforms

  - Mac OSX (xcode)
  - Windows (codeblocks)
  - Linux (codeblocks)

## openFrameworks subversion gets merged frequently into this bundle.



## usage/install

  before using this bundle make sure to follow the setup-
  guide according to your running operation system!

  ## Mac Xcode
	
  - install git
      "port install git-core +svn"
  - install Xcode
      "http://developer.apple.com/TOOLS/xcode/"
	
  ## Windows Codeblocks
	
  - install git
      "http://code.google.com/p/msysgit/"
  - install quicktime
      "http://www.apple.com/de/quicktime/download/"
  - install codeblocks
      "http://www.openframeworks.cc/setup/codeblocks_setup_guide"

	
  ## Linux Codeblocks - Debian (lenny)
	
  - please follow openframeworks.cc/setup/ on how-to install codeblocks


